					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Seems like a waste of time to do every frame, unless you're actually changing the palette that quickly. If you did it every other frame, and had other tasks that were performed every other frame as well, you'd be able to interleave the two. Or maybe you could do something round-robin, where you update 1/4 of the palette each frame, and cycle through quarters, so that the entire palette is updated over four frames.</div>

